Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.90,0:00:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲開 躲開 快跳船
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.66,0:00:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下搞不好要完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.37,0:00:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 剛才那下我家附近炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.13,0:00:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.68,0:01:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.97,0:01:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.52,0:01:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.53,0:01:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱撒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.41,0:01:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.62,0:01:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.33,0:01:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請帶來…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.46,0:01:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的安寧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.82,0:02:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 駿駿 沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去救大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駿駿 師傅他們就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:03:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前 巴哈姆特那混蛋出現時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我答應一個女人會保護好她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.87,0:04:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果我放棄了她的生命選擇了這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 你會選哪邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,選他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去快回 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界會變成什麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事你根本不需要考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狠狠揍一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我幹掉那傢伙之後還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.79,0:05:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這條命隨你們處置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.21,0:05:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下 祝你出師大捷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口是心非
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下一到多洛莫斯立刻撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快撐不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全軍集中力量防守
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.85,0:07:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要撐住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一刻等好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你要獻上生命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就陪你一起獻上生命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒必要跟著送死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.30,0:09:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是我的生命還是你的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕對不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿米拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.37,0:12:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死…死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們得救啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個怪物真的死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.33,0:12:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是我引以為傲的徒弟哦 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.09,0:13:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽可否安好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如今仍在過著王都的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王都因復興工程變得非常繁忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.69,0:13:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得知你那邊沒怎麼遭受巴哈姆特的危害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.32,0:13:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倍感安心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天 發生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.92,0:13:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必我這輩子都不會忘記那天發生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該不會忘的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為英雄的國王從那天起便失明了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過他還在當國王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊的 打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了 王都的人類跟惡魔之間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仇恨消失 和好如初…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.84,0:14:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 不像之前 如今已沒有奴隸什麼的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許關係正在逐漸改變
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貞德離開了王都
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:52.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說現在住在神界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:55.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算回老家之後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再讓奶奶馱著我去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.08,0:15:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惡魔阿薩謝爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴卡斯還是老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.60,0:15:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我當成家人 溫柔地接納了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.52,0:15:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 小姑娘 歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算賴到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你們倆也來幫幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗塔在那天失去了重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過現在已經完全振作起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還給我做了美昧的飯菜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘的話音…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.01,0:16:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然無法恢復啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 想不到代價竟是話音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是叫你們來幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.48,0:16:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的好意我心領了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.55,0:16:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個真好喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不嫌棄的話 我可以教你怎麼做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:16:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 代替我給那個醉鬼做如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.69,0:16:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴卡斯喜歡索菲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索菲大人怎麼可能給這種冒牌神做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.03,0:17:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說誰是冒牌神啊 蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們別跟著起鬨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋…別笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有機會我會向媽媽介紹這些出色的人的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說你蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.97,0:17:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦 我可沒做你那份料理哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遺憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 我今天不是來喝酒的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.15,0:17:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得是時候出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原本就不喜歡王都這地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是回歸放浪生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.93,0:18:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是乎 我明天早上就啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.03,0:18:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.49,0:18:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想讓我給你個擁抱什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候 見到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？見誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在巴哈姆特的光芒中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.27,0:19:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,見到女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,她希望你……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,過得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.81,0:19:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風往哪邊吹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:19:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來到王都之後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:20:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開心的事 快樂的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悲傷得讓人想哭的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各式各樣的事發生了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今後還會過得很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.39,0:23:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴哈姆特根本沒死
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.89,0:23:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 阿米拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.31,0:23:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法瓦羅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.91,0:23:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.63,0:23:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就能重逢的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.91,0:24:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴哈巴哈巴哈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝收看

